<h1 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-Capability:Retrievingthelistofarrangements"><s=
pan style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capability:<span class=3D"fab=
ric-text-color-mark">&nbsp;Retrieving the list of arrangements</span></stro=
ng></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-POST/arrangements"><span>POST /</span>arrangem=
ents</h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves all accounts that the user is entitled to.</p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><strong><u>Feb 2026 ERM changes:</u=
></strong></span> <span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><strong>As part of F=
eb 2026 ERM requirements, this endpoint verb will be changed to POST instea=
d of GET. This is mainly because,&nbsp;<span data-teams=3D"true">ISG has ra=
ised a concern stating the endpoint can be abused if we include searchFilte=
r in the query string parameter, so instead, it should be changed to POST m=
ethod and the seachFilter will have to be included in the request body.&nbs=
p;</span></strong></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><strong><span data-teams=3D"true"><=
u>Feb 2026 ERM changes related to division:</u> The endpoint will be enhanc=
ed to accept a new query string parameter: <code>divisionId</code>.&nbsp;If=
 <code>divisionId</code> is provided, it will be passed to the <code>GetAcc=
ountIdsFromPdpQueryResult</code> API(PDP) to retrieve account IDs associate=
d with that division. If not provided, the endpoint will continue to follow=
 the existing logic. This enhanced endpoint will be used in the following d=
ivisions feature: <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/=
ARTC/SD%3A+Sub-Orgs%28Divisions%29+Channels#SD:SubOrgs(Divisions)Channels-A=
ccountsMFE" rel=3D"nofollow">SD: Sub-Orgs(Divisions) Channels - AccountsMFE=
</a></span></strong></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-11534312" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-11534312" cla=
ss=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-11534312"=
 class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expand=
ed=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-11534312"><span class=3D"expa=
nd-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=3D"t=
rue"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Details o=
f retrieving the list of arrangements</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-11534312" class=3D"expand-conte=
nt" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-11534312">
