<p>It should be an optional parameter</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>value type is =
string</span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><code data-application=3D"com.atlassian.bitbu=
cket-server" data-language=3D"yaml">It can be of this pattern ^[\w-]+$</cod=
e></p><p><span style=3D"font-family: SFMono-Medium , SF Mono , Segoe UI Mon=
o , Roboto Mono , Ubuntu Mono , Menlo , Courier , monospace;">Max length sh=
ould be 50 and this scopeId</span><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">&n=
bsp;is received as a response from the GET /accountGroups API response.</sp=
an></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51=
);"><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">FEB2026</s=
pan></span></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51=
