<h3 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-ExtractingAccountIDs">Extracting Account IDs</=
h3>
<p>An interim solution from one the below will be used <em><u>after ISG's a=
pproval</u></em>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Storing account IDs as a secret in EXP API<br>
 Using Vault to store account IDs</li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-InputValidation">Input Validation</h3>
<p>The below validations should be done on the extracted account IDs.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
