<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Comment</th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">1</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Either of BSB or account number in <u><strong>An=
y</strong></u> of the account IDs have incorrect format</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Return 400</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">2</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">No account ID received</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Return 200 with empty arrangements objects</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h3 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-DownstreamAPIInfo(Feb2026ERMdivisionschanges)"=
>Downstream API Info(Feb 2026 ERM divisions changes)</h3>
<p>If the divisionId is supplied as part of the request, the&nbsp;<code>Get=
AccountIdsFromPdpQueryResult</code> API request should include the division=
Id to ensure PDP will query and return the accountIDs associated with the s=
upplied division and&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">if<span>&nb=
sp;</span></span><code>divisionId</code><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77)=
;"><span>&nbsp;</span>is not provided in the request body, the endpoint wil=
l follow the existing logic</span>.</p>
<ul>
<li>PDPQueryAPI to be uplifted: <code>GetAccountIdsFromPdpQueryResult</code=
></li>
<li>PDPQueryAPI Request</li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "query": [
        {
            "attribute": "RequestAttributes.AccountId"
        }
    ],
    "context": {
        "action": "QUERY",
        "attributes": {
            "RequestAttributes.CustomerUserId": "07a975e0-0a90-4e1c-96d1-c2=
a1e5dcc5a2",
            "RequestAttributes.OrganisationId": "32896172",
            "RequestAttributes.ScopeId": "a39d00a7-8710-4333-adbf-bb82e8c7c=
afg",
            "RequestAttributes.DivisionId": "a39d00a7-8710-4333-adbf-bb82e8=
c9bacf",
            "RequestAttributes.RequestAction": "VIEW_ACCOUNT"
        }
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<ul>
<li>PDPQueryAPI response: There will be no change in the response payload, =
PDP will continue to return the same response payload as earlier.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
