<h3 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-5.3.InputValidation">5.3. Input Validation</h3=
>
<p>The provided account(s) should be checked against the accounts the user =
is entitled to operate on.</p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 55.=
9695%;" data-snooker-col-series=3D"numbers" data-snooker-locked-cols=3D"0">
