<h1 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-Capability:Retrievingtheinterestandtaxsummaryf=
ormultipleaccounts"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capabil=
ity:<span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> Retrieving the interest and tax=
 summary for multiple accounts&nbsp;</span></strong></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-POST/taxAndInterestList"><span style=3D"letter=
-spacing: -0.008em;">POST /taxAndInterestList&nbsp;</span></h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves a list of tax and interest summary for,</p>
<ul>
<li>All accounts / account group that the user is entitled to(if no Account=
IDs are supplied in the request body).</li>
<li><s>List of accountIds supplied as part of the request body(the request =
body to include accountName as well to avoid making extra calls to retrieve=
 the accountName when returning the Exp API response)&nbsp;</s></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><strong><u>Feb 2026 ERM changes:<sp=
an>&nbsp;</span></u></strong><strong>As part of Feb 2026 ERM requirements, =
this endpoint verb will be changed to POST instead of GET. This is mainly b=
ecause,&nbsp;<span data-teams=3D"true">ISG has raised a concern stating the=
 endpoint can be abused if we include searchFilter in the query string para=
meter, so instead, it should be changed to POST method and the seachFilter =
will have to be included in the request body.</span><span data-teams=3D"tru=
e">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span data-teams=3D"true"><=
u>Feb 2026 ERM changes related to division:</u>&nbsp;The endpoint will be e=
xtended to accept a new query string parameter:&nbsp;<code>divisionId</code=
>.&nbsp;If&nbsp;<code>divisionId</code>&nbsp;is provided, it will be passed=
 to the&nbsp;<code>GetAccountIdsFromPdpQueryResult</code>&nbsp;API(PDP) to =
retrieve account IDs associated with that division. If not provided, the en=
dpoint will continue to follow the existing logic. This enhanced endpoint w=
ill be used in the following divisions feature: <a href=3D"https://confluen=
ce.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/SD%3A+Sub-Orgs%28Divisions%29+Channels#S=
D:SubOrgs(Divisions)Channels-Interestandtaxsummary" rel=3D"nofollow">SD: Su=
b-Orgs(Divisions) Channels - Interestandtaxsummary</a></span></span></stron=
g></p>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1876586952" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1876586952" c=
