<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-POST/taxAndInterestDetail"><span>POST /taxAndI=
nterestDetail</span></h2>
<pre><br></pre>
<p>This endpoint retrieves past 3 FYs tax and interest data for an account =
that the user is entitled to.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Downstream API:</p>
<ol>
<li>POST /interests/accountIds&nbsp;<br>
<ol>
<li>retrieve the tax and interest of a single account</li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2. POST <span>/interests/accountId/accruals</=
span></p>
<ol>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
<ol>
<li><span>retrieve the debit / credit accruals since last posting&nbsp;</sp=
an></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/pages/viewpage.action?p=
ageId=3D1947332258" rel=3D"nofollow">Account Interest &amp; Tax Details Inf=
ormation API - Westpac One Core - Westpac Enterprise Confluence</a></p>
<p><br></p>
