<h3 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-ExtractingAccountIDs.2">Extracting Account IDs=
</h3>
<p>An interim solution from one the below will be used <em><u>after ISG's a=
pproval</u></em>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Storing account IDs as a secret in EXP API<br>
 Using Vault to store account IDs</li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-InputValidation.6">Input Validation</h3>
<p>The below validations should be done on the extracted account IDs.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 39.=
7889%;" data-snooker-col-series=3D"numbers" data-snooker-locked-cols=3D"0">
