<h1 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-Capability:Searchforalistofarrangementsfacilit=
ies/rates(Feb2026ERM)"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capa=
bility: Search for a list of arrangements facilities / rates (Feb 2026 ERM)=
</strong></span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxyaccountv2-POST/arrangements/interestFacilities">POST /ar=
rangements/interestFacilities</h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves the facilities and rate detail for a given Accou=
ntID supplied as part of the request body. It's introduced as part of the S=
D <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/pages/viewpage.action?pa=
geId=3D2106501912" rel=3D"nofollow">09. SD: Overdraft (Arranged &amp; IDOL)=
 Limits and Pricing - Westpac One Core - Westpac Enterprise Confluence</a> =
and a new W1C endpoint will be added as the downstream of this endpoint.&nb=
sp;</p>
<p><br></p>
